{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525410/extras/welcome_en.png?t=1737922138\" /><br><br>Welcome to Motel 86. Located in the heart of the desert, our motel is the perfect choice for travelers looking for a comfortable and convenient place to stay while enjoying their trip <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525410/extras/story_en.png?t=1737922138\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525410/extras/explore.gif?t=1737922138\" /><br><br>Imagine waking up trapped in an abandoned motel. When you manage to get out of the room, a phone rings in the distance. <br><br>This is a first person point &amp; click adventure in 3D with touches of terror. In order to progress through the game, you will have to use your wit to explore the corridors, rooms, offices and the diner to find objects and solve puzzles will help you escape and find out what happened there.<br><br>You will have to use your wit to solve puzzles and find out what happened.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525410/extras/gameplay_en.png?t=1737922138\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Psychological terror: </strong> The motel is not a safe place. If you think you are alone, think again.<br><br></li><li><strong>Explore the motel: </strong> You can move freely around the motel. However, you will have access to more (even very hidden) parts of the motel as you progress through the story.<br><br></li><li><strong>Puzzles, puzzles and more puzzles: </strong> If you want to escape, you will have to use your wit to solve the puzzles scattered throughout the motel. Sometimes you will have to use previously collected items, and other times you only have to use your brain to find the logic around the mechanisms.</li></ul>","backg